## Notes

Migration completed successfully. All phases have been executed and verified.

## Rollback Plan

In case of issues:

1. Keep backup of original structure until migration is complete
2. Document all changes in a separate changelog
3. Test new structure thoroughly before removing old files
4. Maintain list of all file movements for easy rollback
